SELECT end.totalflow - start.totalflow FROM
(SELECT ftotal-rtotal totalflow FROM wt4300gprsdata WHERE flowId = ${num} AND TIME > ${startDate} AND TIME  < ${endDate} ORDER BY TIME ASC LIMIT 1) START,
(SELECT ftotal-rtotal totalflow FROM wt4300gprsdata WHERE flowId = ${num} AND TIME > ${startDate} AND TIME  <  ${endDate} ORDER BY TIME DESC LIMIT 1) END;

